<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Luapin Aja</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<style>
    html, body { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; background: #fdfdff; overflow-x: hidden; width: 100%; }
    .glass-nav { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); }
    
    .blob-wrapper { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100vw; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; z-index: -1; pointer-events: none; }
    .blob { position: absolute; filter: blur(60px); opacity: 0.6; animation: float 10s infinite ease-in-out alternate; }
    .blob-1 { top: -5%; left: -10%; width: 250px; height: 250px; background: #e0e7ff; border-radius: 50%; }
    .blob-2 { bottom: -5%; right: -10%; width: 300px; height: 300px; background: #fce7f3; border-radius: 50%; animation-delay: -5s; }
    
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .blob { filter: blur(80px); }
        .blob-1 { top: -10%; left: -10%; width: 400px; height: 400px; }
        .blob-2 { bottom: -10%; right: -10%; width: 500px; height: 500px; }
    }
    
    @keyframes float { 0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); } 100% { transform: translate(20px, 30px) scale(1.05); } }
    .btn-mewah { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #3b82f6 100%); transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    .btn-mewah:hover { box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .icon-fill { font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="text-slate-800 min-h-screen flex flex-col relative" oncontextmenu="return false;">

<div class="blob-wrapper">
    <div class="blob blob-1"></div>
    <div class="blob blob-2"></div>
</div>

<nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-40 glass-nav">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto flex justify-between items-center h-16 px-6">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 group">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-indigo-600 icon-fill text-[28px] group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">psychology_alt</span>
            <div class="text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-blue-500">Luapin Aja</div>
        </a>
        <div class="hidden sm:flex items-center gap-6">
            <a href="/jelajah" class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Jelajah</a>
            <a href="/tulis" class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-indigo-600 transition-colors">Tulis Pesan</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<main class="flex-grow flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-5 sm:px-6 pt-32 pb-24 text-center max-w-[800px] w-full mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-extrabold rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 sm:mb-8 border border-indigo-100 shadow-sm">
        Tanpa Jejak, Bebas Bercerita
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-tight">
        Luapin <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-blue-500">Aja</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 max-w-[600px] mx-auto mb-10 sm:mb-12 leading-relaxed px-2">
        Ruang aman untuk melepas beban pikiran. Bagikan kisahmu, baca pengalaman orang lain, dan saling memberi tanggapan. 100% anonim tanpa perlu login.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 w-full px-2 sm:px-0">
        <a href="/jelajah" class="btn-mewah px-8 py-3.5 text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">explore</span> Jelajahi Cerita
        </a>
        <a href="/tulis" class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-white text-slate-700 text-sm font-bold rounded-full shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]">edit_square</span> Tulis Pesan
        </a>
    </div>
</main>

<footer class="w-full text-center py-6 border-t border-slate-100 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm z-10 mt-auto">
    <p class="text-[11px] sm:text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 tracking-wide">Copyright &copy; 2026 AP. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
